      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim the green stalks off your <strong>aubergine[s]</strong></p><p>Cut the<strong> aubergine[s]</strong> in half lengthways, then score the flesh in a criss-cross pattern, taking care not to cut through to the skin</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1679331143025-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1679331143025-x400.jpg",
