            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>aubergine halves</strong> to a <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!) then drizzle over <strong>half</strong> the <strong>hoisin marinade </strong>(save the rest for later!)</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 25-30 min or until the aubergine is tender – this is your <strong>hoisin</strong> <strong>roasted aubergine</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1679331146558-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1679331146558-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1679331146558-x700.jpg",
